# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HireSight — Environment Variables
#
# Copy this file to .dev.vars for local development:
#   cp .env.example .dev.vars
#
# For production, set secrets via Wrangler (never commit real values):
#   wrangler secret put JWT_SECRET
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# JWT signing secret — MUST be changed before deployment.
# Generate a strong value with: openssl rand -hex 32
JWT_SECRET=replace_this_with_a_strong_random_secret_at_least_32_chars

# ─── Cloudflare Bindings (configured in wrangler.toml, not here) ─────────────
#
# The following are declared in wrangler.toml and auto-provisioned by Cloudflare.
# They are listed here for documentation purposes only.
#
# DB              → D1 database binding  (database_name = "hiring_db")
# VECTORIZE       → Vectorize index      (index_name    = "resumes_index")
# AI              → Workers AI binding
# LEADERBOARD     → Durable Object namespace (LeaderboardDO)
